{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":840,"text":"I want to introduce you to some\nvery wise kids that I've known,"},{"time":5480,"text":"but first I want\nto introduce you to a camel."},{"time":8720,"text":"This is Cassie, a therapy camel\nvisiting one of our young patients"},{"time":13000,"text":"in her room,"},{"time":14920,"text":"which is pretty magical."},{"time":17880,"text":"A friend of mine raises camels\nat his ranch in the Santa Cruz Mountains."},{"time":23040,"text":"He has about eight of them,"},{"time":24720,"text":"and he started 30 years ago"},{"time":26440,"text":"because he thought\nhorses were too mundane."},{"time":29400,"text":"John is an out-of-the-box thinker,"},{"time":32800,"text":"which explains why the two of us\nhave been such good friends"},{"time":35640,"text":"all of our lives."},{"time":38200,"text":"Over the years, I've convinced him\nto shuttle those sweet furry beasts"},{"time":43360,"text":"up to hang out with our sick kids\nfrom time to time."},{"time":47440,"text":"Talking to John, I was surprised to learn"},{"time":49880,"text":"that camels have an average\nlife expectancy of 40 to 50 years."},{"time":55600,"text":"The life expectancy of many\nof the children with whom I work"},{"time":59120,"text":"is less than a year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61520,"text":"This is a picture\nof the George Mark Children's House,"},{"time":64599,"text":"the first pediatric\npalliative respite care center"},{"time":68120,"text":"to open in the United States."},{"time":70400,"text":"I founded it in 2004,"},{"time":73400,"text":"after years of working as a psychologist"},{"time":76360,"text":"on pediatric intensive care units,"},{"time":79080,"text":"frustrated with the undignified deaths\nthat so many children experienced"},{"time":84120,"text":"and their families had to endure."},{"time":86960,"text":"As I sat with families whose children\nwere at the end of their lives,"},{"time":91160,"text":"I was acutely aware of our surroundings."},{"time":94840,"text":"While the elevated train\nrumbled overhead on its track,"},{"time":98880,"text":"quite literally the room reverberated\nwith each passing train car."},{"time":104480,"text":"The lights on the ward\nwere fluorescent and too bright."},{"time":107880,"text":"Monitors beeped, as did the elevator,"},{"time":111120,"text":"noisily announcing its arrival."},{"time":113880,"text":"These families were experiencing"},{"time":115880,"text":"some of the most excruciating\nmoments of their lives,"},{"time":119520,"text":"and I so wanted them\nto have a more peaceful place"},{"time":123120,"text":"in which to say a last goodbye\nto their young daughters and sons."},{"time":127480,"text":"Surely, I thought,"},{"time":129960,"text":"there must be a better spot\nthan a hospital intensive care unit"},{"time":133600,"text":"for children at the end of their lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136720,"text":"Our children's house"},{"time":139520,"text":"is calm and nurturing."},{"time":142040,"text":"It's a place where families\ncan stay together"},{"time":144680,"text":"to enjoy quality time with their children,"},{"time":147280,"text":"many of whom are there for respite stays,"},{"time":150040,"text":"some with repeated visits\nover a span of many years."},{"time":153600,"text":"We call those kids our frequent flyers."},{"time":158360,"text":"Rather than the bright,\nnoisy quarters of the hospital,"},{"time":161800,"text":"their rooms are calm and comfortable,"},{"time":164640,"text":"with actual living spaces\nfor the families,"},{"time":167920,"text":"a sanctuary of gardens"},{"time":169720,"text":"and a wonderful outdoor playground"},{"time":172240,"text":"with special structures\nfor children with physical limitations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177040,"text":"This sweet baby Lars"},{"time":179400,"text":"came to us directly\nfrom a hospital intensive care unit."},{"time":184440,"text":"Imagine hearing the heartbreaking news"},{"time":187600,"text":"that none of us would ever want to hear."},{"time":190360,"text":"His parents had been told\nthat Lars had a brain anomaly"},{"time":194120,"text":"that would keep him from ever swallowing,"},{"time":196960,"text":"walking, talking"},{"time":198880,"text":"or developing mentally."},{"time":201480,"text":"Recognizing what little chance\nhe had for survival,"},{"time":204480,"text":"his parents chose\nto focus on the quality of time"},{"time":207560,"text":"that they could spend together."},{"time":209600,"text":"They moved into\none of our family apartments"},{"time":212200,"text":"and treasured each day that they had,"},{"time":214640,"text":"which were far too few."},{"time":217000,"text":"Lars's life was brief, to be sure,"},{"time":219880,"text":"mere weeks,"},{"time":221520,"text":"but it was calm and comfortable."},{"time":224080,"text":"He went on hikes with his parents."},{"time":226920,"text":"The time that he spent in the pool\nwith our aquatic therapist"},{"time":229920,"text":"lessened the seizures he was experiencing"},{"time":232120,"text":"and helped him to sleep at night."},{"time":234320,"text":"His family had a peaceful place"},{"time":236400,"text":"in which to both celebrate his life"},{"time":238800,"text":"and mourn his death."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241040,"text":"It has been five years\nsince Lars was with us,"},{"time":244280,"text":"and in that time,"},{"time":246200,"text":"his family has welcomed"},{"time":248560,"text":"a daughter and another son."},{"time":251280,"text":"They are such a powerful testament"},{"time":254240,"text":"to the positive outcome that specialized\nchildren's hospice care can create."},{"time":259640,"text":"Their baby's physical discomfort\nwas well managed,"},{"time":262320,"text":"giving all of them the gift of time\nto be together in a beautiful place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":268280,"text":"I'm going to talk to you now"},{"time":270320,"text":"about the elephant"},{"time":271560,"text":"rather than the camel in the room."},{"time":275440,"text":"Very few people want to talk about death,"},{"time":278600,"text":"and even fewer about children's death."},{"time":285680,"text":"Loss of a child,"},{"time":288080,"text":"especially for those of us\nwho have our own children,"},{"time":290680,"text":"is frightening,"},{"time":292800,"text":"more than frightening,"},{"time":294840,"text":"paralyzing,"},{"time":296920,"text":"debilitating,"},{"time":298920,"text":"impossible."},{"time":301320,"text":"But what I've learned is this:"},{"time":303600,"text":"children don't stop dying"},{"time":305640,"text":"just because we the adults"},{"time":307640,"text":"can't comprehend\nthe injustice of losing them."},{"time":311000,"text":"And what's more,"},{"time":313520,"text":"if we can be brave enough"},{"time":315320,"text":"to face the possibility of death,"},{"time":317200,"text":"even among the most innocent,"},{"time":320120,"text":"we gain an unparalleled kind of wisdom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324240,"text":"Take Crystal, for example."},{"time":327560,"text":"She was one of the first children\nto come for care"},{"time":329960,"text":"after we opened our doors."},{"time":332280,"text":"She was nine when she arrived,"},{"time":333960,"text":"and her neurologist expected\nthat she might live another two weeks."},{"time":338320,"text":"She had an inoperable brain tumor,"},{"time":340840,"text":"and her decline had really accelerated"},{"time":343600,"text":"in the week before she came to us."},{"time":346240,"text":"After settling into her room,"},{"time":348240,"text":"dressed entirely in pink and lavender,"},{"time":352000,"text":"surrounded by the Hello Kitty\naccessories that she loved,"},{"time":356120,"text":"she spent the next several days"},{"time":358880,"text":"winning over the hearts\nof every staff member."},{"time":362760,"text":"Bit by bit, her condition stabilized,"},{"time":365960,"text":"and then to our astonishment,"},{"time":368400,"text":"she actually improved."},{"time":371160,"text":"There were a variety of factors"},{"time":372840,"text":"that contributed to Crystal's improvement"},{"time":376440,"text":"which we later came to call\nthe \"George Mark bump,\""},{"time":381120,"text":"a lovely, not uncommon phenomenon"},{"time":384000,"text":"where children outlive\nthe prognoses of their illnesses"},{"time":386920,"text":"if they're outside of the hospital."},{"time":390280,"text":"The calmer atmosphere of her surroundings,"},{"time":394520,"text":"tasty meals that were fixed\noften to accommodate her requests,"},{"time":399360,"text":"the resident pets,"},{"time":401640,"text":"the therapy dog and rabbit\nspent lots of cozy time with Crystal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":407160,"text":"After she had been with us\nfor about a week,"},{"time":410120,"text":"she called her grandmother,"},{"time":412040,"text":"and she said,"},{"time":413480,"text":"\"Gee, I'm staying in a great big house,"},{"time":417120,"text":"and there's room for you to come, too."},{"time":420080,"text":"And guess what?"},{"time":421760,"text":"You don't have to bring any quarters"},{"time":423800,"text":"because the washer and dryer are free.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":426080,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":428280,"text":"Crystal's grandmother\nsoon arrived from out of town,"},{"time":431160,"text":"and they spent the remaining\nfour months of Crystal's life"},{"time":435720,"text":"enjoying very special days together."},{"time":438200,"text":"Some days were special because Crystal\nwas outside in her wheelchair"},{"time":442200,"text":"sitting by the fountain."},{"time":444040,"text":"For a little girl who had spent most\nof the year earlier in a hospital bed,"},{"time":448440,"text":"being outside counting hummingbirds"},{"time":451400,"text":"made for an amazing time with her grandma,"},{"time":453760,"text":"and lots of laughter."},{"time":455640,"text":"Other days were special\nbecause of the activities"},{"time":458200,"text":"that our child life specialist\ncreated for her."},{"time":461840,"text":"Crystal strung beads and made jewelry\nfor everybody in the house."},{"time":466040,"text":"She painted a pumpkin\nto help decorate for Halloween."},{"time":470360,"text":"She spent many excited days\nplanning her tenth birthday,"},{"time":474720,"text":"which of course none of us\nthought she would ever see."},{"time":479000,"text":"All of us wore pink boas for the occasion,"},{"time":482160,"text":"and Crystal, as you can see,"},{"time":484720,"text":"queen for a day,"},{"time":485960,"text":"wore a sparkly tiara."}]},{"cues":[{"time":488640,"text":"One hot morning, I arrived at work"},{"time":490400,"text":"and Crystal and her partner\nin crime, Charlie, greeted me."},{"time":495920,"text":"With some help, they had set up\na lemonade and cookie stand"},{"time":499080,"text":"outside the front door,"},{"time":501000,"text":"a very strategic location."},{"time":505320,"text":"I asked Crystal the price\nof the cookie that I had selected,"},{"time":508720,"text":"and she said, \"Three dollars.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":511280,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":515159,"text":"I said that seemed a bit high\nfor one cookie."}]},{"cues":[{"time":518280,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":520039,"text":"It was small."},{"time":523320,"text":"\"I know,\" she acknowledged with a grin,"},{"time":526040,"text":"\"but I'm worth it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":529000,"text":"And therein lie the words of wisdom"},{"time":530920,"text":"of a young girl whose brief life\nforever impacted mine."},{"time":536800,"text":"Crystal was worth it,"},{"time":539080,"text":"and shouldn't every child whose life\nis shortened by a horrific illness"},{"time":544400,"text":"be worth it?"},{"time":546040,"text":"Together, all of us today"},{"time":548280,"text":"can offer that same specialized care\nthat Crystal received"},{"time":551560,"text":"by recognizing that children's\nrespite and hospice care"},{"time":557240,"text":"is a critical component missing\nfrom our healthcare landscape."},{"time":563555,"text":"It's also interesting to note"},{"time":564960,"text":"that we are able to provide this care"},{"time":566800,"text":"at about one third of the cost\nof a hospital intensive care unit,"},{"time":571320,"text":"and our families don't see a bill."},{"time":574880,"text":"We are ever grateful to the supporters"},{"time":577680,"text":"who believe in this important work\nthat we're doing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":582000,"text":"The truth is that my colleagues and I"},{"time":585480,"text":"and the parents and other family members"},{"time":589080,"text":"who get to experience this special wisdom"},{"time":592080,"text":"are in a unique position."},{"time":594880,"text":"There are only two freestanding\npediatric hospices in the United States,"},{"time":600120,"text":"although I'm happy to report\nthat based on our model,"},{"time":602840,"text":"there are 18 others\nunder various stages of development."}]},{"cues":[{"time":606920,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":611440,"text":"Still, most of the children\nwho die in the United States every year"},{"time":616480,"text":"die in hospital rooms,"},{"time":618520,"text":"surrounded by beeping machines"},{"time":620960,"text":"and anxious, exhausted adults"},{"time":623080,"text":"who have no other option"},{"time":625080,"text":"but to say goodbye\nunder those harsh, institutional lights"},{"time":628920,"text":"and among virtual strangers."},{"time":631800,"text":"For comparison's sake,"},{"time":633960,"text":"the United Kingdom,"},{"time":635320,"text":"which is a country with about one fifth\nthe population of the United States,"},{"time":639480,"text":"and about half the size\nof the state of California,"},{"time":643120,"text":"has 54 hospice and respite centers."},{"time":649840,"text":"Why is that?"},{"time":651720,"text":"I've asked myself that question\nobviously many times."},{"time":656520,"text":"My best guess is that Americans,\nwith our positive can-do attitude"},{"time":662040,"text":"hold the expectation\nthat our medical care system will fix it,"},{"time":666640,"text":"even though it may be a childhood illness\nfor which there is no cure."},{"time":671760,"text":"We go to extraordinary measures\nto keep children alive"},{"time":675880,"text":"when in fact the greatest kindness\nthat we might give them"},{"time":679280,"text":"would be a peaceful, pain-free"},{"time":682040,"text":"end of life."},{"time":684400,"text":"The transition from cure to care"},{"time":687240,"text":"remains a challenging one\nfor many hospital physicians"},{"time":690480,"text":"whose training has really been\nabout saving lives,"},{"time":694000,"text":"not about gently guiding the patient\nto the end of life."},{"time":698640,"text":"The dad of a sweet baby\nfor whom we cared at the end of her life"},{"time":702200,"text":"certainly captured this dichotomy"},{"time":704760,"text":"when he reflected"},{"time":706360,"text":"that there are a lot of people\nto help you bring an infant into the world"},{"time":710360,"text":"but very few to help you usher a baby out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":715120,"text":"So what is the magic ingredient\nat George Mark?"},{"time":719160,"text":"The complex medical diagnoses\nthat bring our young patients to us"},{"time":723280,"text":"mean that their lives\nhave often been restricted,"},{"time":726280,"text":"some to a hospital bed\nfor long periods of time,"},{"time":729040,"text":"others to wheelchairs,"},{"time":730920,"text":"still others to intensive courses\nof chemotherapy or rehab."},{"time":737120,"text":"We make a practice\nof ignoring those limitations."},{"time":740840,"text":"Our default answer is \"yes\""},{"time":743080,"text":"and our default question is, \"Why not?\""},{"time":746480,"text":"That's why we took a young boy"},{"time":748320,"text":"who wasn't going to live\nfor another baseball season"},{"time":751320,"text":"to Game 5 of the World Series."},{"time":754760,"text":"That's why we have a talent show\nput on by the staff and kids"},{"time":758200,"text":"for family and friends."},{"time":759840,"text":"Who wouldn't be enchanted by a young boy\nplaying a piano piece with his feet,"},{"time":764920,"text":"because his arms are atrophied?"},{"time":767800,"text":"That's why we have a prom every year."},{"time":771800,"text":"It's pretty magical."},{"time":773800,"text":"We started the prom"},{"time":775680,"text":"after hearing a dad lament"},{"time":777320,"text":"that he would never pin\na boutonniere on his son's tuxedo lapel."},{"time":783480,"text":"The weeks before the dance,"},{"time":785640,"text":"the house is in a flurry,"},{"time":786920,"text":"and I don't know who's more excited,\nthe staff or the kids."}]},{"cues":[{"time":789720,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":790880,"text":"The night of the event"},{"time":792520,"text":"involves rides in vintage cars,"},{"time":797000,"text":"a walk on a red carpet"},{"time":799000,"text":"into the great room,"},{"time":801520,"text":"a terrific DJ"},{"time":804160,"text":"and a photographer at the ready"},{"time":805960,"text":"to capture pictures of these attendees"},{"time":808520,"text":"and their families."},{"time":810640,"text":"At the end of the evening this year,"},{"time":812960,"text":"one of our young,\ndelightful teenaged girls,"},{"time":817680,"text":"Caitlin, said to her mom,"},{"time":821640,"text":"\"That was the best night\nof my whole life.\""},{"time":824480,"text":"And that's just the point,"},{"time":826880,"text":"to capture the best days and nights,"},{"time":830640,"text":"to abolish limitations,"},{"time":833520,"text":"to have your default answer be \"yes\""},{"time":835680,"text":"and your default question be, \"Why not?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":839800,"text":"Ultimately life is too short,"},{"time":842320,"text":"whether we live\nto be 85 years or just eight."},{"time":845800,"text":"Trust me."},{"time":847080,"text":"Better yet, trust Sam."},{"time":850760,"text":"It's not by pretending\nthat death doesn't exist"},{"time":854880,"text":"that we keep the people,"},{"time":856720,"text":"especially the little people that we love,"},{"time":859160,"text":"safe."},{"time":861080,"text":"In the end,"},{"time":862640,"text":"we can't control how long any of us lives."},{"time":865880,"text":"What we can control"},{"time":867640,"text":"is how we spend our days,"},{"time":870280,"text":"the spaces we create,"},{"time":873120,"text":"the meaning and joy that we make."},{"time":876920,"text":"We cannot change the outcome,"},{"time":879960,"text":"but we can change the journey."},{"time":883680,"text":"Isn't it time"},{"time":887000,"text":"to recognize that children deserve"},{"time":889280,"text":"nothing less than our\nmost uncompromising bravery"},{"time":893680,"text":"and our wildest imagination."}]},{"cues":[{"time":897040,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":898280,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}